==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Struck
<hw>Struck</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <def><pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> of
<er>Strike</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Struck jury</b></col> <fld>(Law)</fld>, <cd>a special
jury, composed of persons having special knowledge or qualifications,
selected by striking from the panel of jurors a certain number for each
party, leaving the number required by law to try the
cause.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strucken</ent>⟦br⟧
